        "type": "html",
        "html": "<p>We&#8217;re closing in on the end of 2018, so it&#8217;s time that we reveal our Game of the Year awards. We have a few listed categories with a whole bunch of nominations. Before we get into it, we would just like to say that 2018 has been an amazing year for gaming and each game listed here has been an absolute blast to play.</p>\n<p><em>Disclaimer: Any game that was released specifically for the Nintendo Switch in 2018 is eligible for nomination. Meaning that if a game had initially released for 2018 but didn&#8217;t arrive on the Switch until this year, it&#8217;s fair game.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Art Design</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Octopath Traveler</li>\n<li>Hollow Knight</li>\n<li>Celeste</li>\n<li>Donkey Kong Country: Tropical Freeze</li>\n<li>The Messenger</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4551\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Art.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Art.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Art.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Art.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Hidden Gem of 2018</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Horizon Shift &#8217;81</li>\n<li>Flat Heroes</li>\n<li>The Low Road</li>\n<li>The Mooseman</li>\n<li>The Bug Butcher</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4555\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Hidden-Gem.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Hidden-Gem.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Hidden-Gem.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Hidden-Gem.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Soundtrack</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Octopath Traveler</li>\n<li>Mario Tennis Aces</li>\n<li>Celeste</li>\n<li>Pokemon: Let&#8217;s Go, Pikachu/Eevee</li>\n<li>Bayonetta 2</li>\n<li>Donkey Kong Country: Tropical Freeze</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4559\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Soundtrack.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Soundtrack.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Soundtrack.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Soundtrack.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best 3DS Game</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Detective Pikachu</li>\n<li>Luigi&#8217;s Mansion</li>\n<li>Sushi Striker</li>\n<li>WarioWare Gold</li>\n<li>Shin Megami Tensei: Journey Redux</li>\n<li>Captain Toad: Treasure Tracker</li>\n<li>Radiant Historia: Perfect Chronology</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4552\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-3DS.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-3DS.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-3DS.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-3DS.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Single Player Experience</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Hollow Knight</li>\n<li>Octopath Traveler</li>\n<li>Starlink: Battle for Atlas</li>\n<li>Bayonetta 2</li>\n<li>Celeste</li>\n<li>Monster Boy and the Cursed Kingdom</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4558\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Single-Player.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Single-Player.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Single-Player.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Single-Player.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Multiplayer/Party Game</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Super Mario Party</li>\n<li>Mario Tennis Aces</li>\n<li>Super Smash Bros. Ultimate</li>\n<li>Kirby Star Allies</li>\n<li>Overcooked 2</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4556\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Multiplayer.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Multiplayer.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Multiplayer.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Multiplayer.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Third-Party Game</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Starlink: Battle for Atlas</li>\n<li>Celeste</li>\n<li>Overcooked 2</li>\n<li>Diablo III</li>\n<li>Dark Souls Remastered</li>\n<li>Hollow Knight</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4561\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Nindie</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Hollow Knight</li>\n<li>Celeste</li>\n<li>Overcooked 2</li>\n<li>Monster Boy and the Cursed Kingdom</li>\n<li>The Messenger</li>\n<li>Dead Cells</li>\n<li>Undertale</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4560\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party-1.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party-1.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party-1.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Third-Party-1.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best DLC</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Mario + Rabbids: Kingdom Battle (DK Adventure)</li>\n<li>Xenoblade Chronicles 2 (Torna the Golden Country)</li>\n<li>Splatoon 2 (Octo Expansion)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4553\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-DLC.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-DLC.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-DLC.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-DLC.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Best Port</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Captain Toad: Treasure Tracker</li>\n<li>Donkey Kong Country: Tropical Freeze</li>\n<li>Hyrule Warriors: Definitive Edition</li>\n<li>Bayonetta 2</li>\n<li>Diablo III</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4557\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Port.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Port.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Port.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-Port.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Switch Game of the Year</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Super Smash Bros. Ultimate</li>\n<li>Pokemon: Let&#8217;s Go, Pikachu/Eevee</li>\n<li>Celeste</li>\n<li>Hollow Knight</li>\n<li>Octopath Traveler</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And the winner is&#8230;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4554\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-GOTY.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" alt=\"Game of the Year\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-GOTY.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-GOTY.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/switchaboo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/GOTY-2018-GOTY.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Do you agree with our selections for the Game of the Year Awards? Let us know in the Comments section below.</p>\n<p>Be sure to <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/switchaboo\">like us on Facebook</a> in order to get updated on every article we post, along with more Nintendo content. And if you&#8217;d like to see more, why not <a href=\"https://switchaboo.com/2018/12/23/horizon-shift-81-review-switch/\">check out the review for Horizon Shift &#8217;81, a nominee for Best Hidden Gem?</a></p>\n"
